      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this absolute beauty! It is in truly incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for the road, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! \u2728",
