    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is an absolute showroom-quality specimen, meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and driven only on fair-weather days. The exterior finish is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like luster entirely free of stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every panel gap is factory-perfect, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary that still retains its original new-car scent. The premium leather upholstery is taut with no bolster wear, the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one, and the dashboard is pristine with no UV fading. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature\u2014including the high-definition infotainment and climate control\u2014operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is indistinguishable from new; the engine bay is spotless, the transmission shifts are buttery smooth, and the suspension provides a firm yet compliant ride. It comes with a comprehensive binder of all service records performed exclusively at the dealership, both original keys, and the factory owner's manual. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade vehicle in impeccable condition.",
      "price": 43800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
